modName: Black Marsh Import - Models and Textures
summary: Here is a collection of weapons that I did which can be used for Skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
I plan on making more weapons, but I need someone to implement these into the game. I have trouble doing so.

The pack contains 5 weapons so far with their own unique looks.

Obsidian Warhammer
Bone Talon Dagger
Silver Jagged Katana

Steel Great Cleaver

If all goes well I'll make some more.

Check out my blog for latest progress:
http://artiedee.blogspot.co.uk/
author: artiedee
